Module jdk.compiler
Package com.sun.source.tree

Interface MemberReferenceTree

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExpressionTree, Tree
    public interface MemberReferenceTree
extends ExpressionTree
    A tree node for a member reference expression. For example: 
       expression # [ identifier | new ]
    Since:
    1.8
